data.description: Begin your fantastic Florida boating lifestyle from this charming pool home with a fishing dock, boat lift, and timeless water views. This meticulously maintained home is nestled in a prime Palm Coast location with easy access to the Matanzas River. Inside you will find many upgrades and adornments to include beautiful tile flooring in the living areas and custom closets. The open kitchen will delight the chef of the family with ample cabinetry, beautiful granite countertops, stainless appliances, and a charming tile backsplash. But the excitement really starts as you enter the pool deck overlooking the saltwater canal. There is a 10,000 lb lift, an upgraded sea wall, new screen on the pool enclosure, and new pool deck surfacing. The tile roof is 2018, and the windows and doors were new in 2016. Bring your boat and start enjoying this spectacular coastal property before Summer!
